Package com.nokia.j2me.pim

Interface Summary
ContactChangeListener ContactChangeListener enables an application to discover when there are contact changes, please refer to ContactChange.
 

Class Summary
ContactChange This class describe one contact change, the fields that are contained in one contact change.
ContactChangeManager ContactChangeManger is used to manage receiving contact changes when requester application is running or history contact change when it is not running
